Welcome to ReHeaT 2

the Reference for the Heart failure Transcriptome

Overview

ReHeaT is a user friendly portal to explore and query the consensus multicellular program of human end-stage heart failure.

This multicellular program has been derived from four single nuc studies and has been integrated with 20 bulk studies to identify robust deregulation patterns in heart failure.

Data overview
